Milestones for MHSVLC 0.1
=========================

GUI
===

1. Play/Pause
2. Forward
3. backward
4. Playback Slider with time elapsed and total time
5. Volume Control Slider
6. Fullscreen
7. Show Meta: Name/Title, Author, Album, Artwork
8. UI Splash at start

Playlist
========

1. List
2. Now Playing Only
3. Minimal Library feature

File Access
===========

1. From a fixed dir...

Intended Codes/formats
======================

1. Audio: mp3, wav, midi, ogg/flac
2. Video: avi, mp4
3. Image: PNG, JPG, GIF


Current Status/Progress
=======================

1. Unstable Port VLC 0.9.9a
2. Libmad ported, plays low bit mp3 out of the box
3. Jerky sound output, working on a better Producer Consumer implementation b/w:
   | Audio File -> Decoder -> Output Buffer | => Hardware
4. GUI development started

Future Possibility (Working on it) 
==================

1. Python on S60 may be
2. No Qt (enough overhead)
3. Gstreamer ma replace the whole libVLC stuff


